data.description: Cozy and quaint ranch style manufactured home hidden amongst the evergreen and aspen trees! If you are looking for a rental investment property, private get away retreat or full-time residence, this property has it all. The 2 bedroom, 2 bath home has an open plan with a cozy wood fireplace to set the mood. The outbuildings are perfect for goats, chickens, horses and other furry and feathered friends.  The wildlife is abundant!  Located in Ranch of the Rockies near the top of Trout Creek Pass on two lots totaling 5 acres. With a second lot included this property has excellent potential.  You are close to world class fishing, hiking, ATV trails, skiing, and biking. Property is private but close to Buena Vista and Breckenridge ski area.  Colorado Springs and Denver are a short drive away.  HOA includes central trash service, dog park, pavilion, and a stocked fishing reservoir for all property owners and guests.
